text: Miloslav Švaříček (born 14 February 1942) is a Czech skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1964 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Czechoslovakia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:People from Nové Město na Moravě
